{"tid":1650400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"舞王護駕扮李小龍練功 網民極玻璃心：佢香港長大，侮辱大陸？","createTime":"2019-10-13T02:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T02:51:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff05226677d08977ce76525267c2c3b35242c9f0","tid":1650400,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:49:40.000Z","msg":"火箭總經理莫利（Daryl Morey）的撐港言論引發全中國打壓NBA，正當中美關係緊張的時候，火箭兩位球星夏登（James Harden）及韋斯卜克（Russell Westbrook）急忙道歉，成功取悅中國網民。今夏離開湖人轉戰CBA的「舞王」L史堤軒臣（Lance Stephenson），此時也在網上貼出自己模仿李小龍練功的樣子，當然獲得中國網民讚揚。<br />\n<br />\nL史堤軒臣今夏離開湖人後，未獲球隊青睞，輾轉到中國大陸賺人仔。而賺中國人的錢，當然要取悅中國人，他日前在IG上載了自己的練功照，寫道：「李小龍的誕生之地&mdash;&mdash;中國！」在李小龍的世代，大家都以中國人的身份驕傲，香港歌手組合大懶堂（LMF）更創作一首名為《1127》的歌曲，紀念這位功夫傳奇。不過，今天中國人的身份，卻不是每個人都想擁有。<br />\n<br />\n舞王這張照片收到的反應不一，有網民說：「昔日性格暴躁的惡漢，現在已經變成一股清泉。」又讚揚他「很帥」、「練我們大中華的武術」等等，他去季在湖人的隊友古斯馬（Kyle Kuzma）也留下「笑喊」的表情。惟有中國網民真的極度「玻璃心」，李小龍在美國舊金山出世，在香港長大，舞王此帖被諷刺：「李小龍在香港長大，是在侮辱大陸嗎？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191011/large/1570794814_fed9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191011%2Flarge%2F1570794814_fed9.jpg&h=9cd07d49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20191011/60143859\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191011%2F60143859&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=3ae958ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191011%2F60143859&h=c3357cc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20191011/60143859</a>"},{"pid":"03dac47118fbd9511f1d9effdfd6ac2e502529bd","tid":1650400,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:49:48.000Z","msg":"<ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大埔人 <br />\n今日 1400<br />\n 大埔超級城見</span></span></div></ins><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em><ins>⚠️最新活動 ⚠️<br />\n倒數美國就香港人權民主法進行審議<br />\n香港人權民主法案集氣大會<br />\n#1014USA<br />\n<br />\n日期：10月14日<br />\n時間：晚上7點<br />\n地點：遮打花園</ins></em></span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <ins> <div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 公民抗爭式交稅<br />\n<br />\n香港人真 &middot; 反抗！！！<br />\n<br />\n入黎跟住做啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n＞【<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637669】＜\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637669】＜</a></div></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idNDLoL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidNDLoL.jpg&h=7fd20403&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9edd872709fefa336b9490a6189e036306f76dd8","tid":1650400,"uid":297334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:51:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i69Oods.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi69Oods.png&h=62b806c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ENv59Tt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FENv59Tt.png&h=ab5a5de9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMjuR6P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMjuR6P.png&h=7114c566&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}